4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning Bootcamp designed for beginners with no prior experience. This 16-week course features hands-on learning, involving Python, SQL, Streamlit, and various statistics applications, enabling students to become proficient Data Analysts. Students will delve into predictive models and algorithms, tackle real-life case studies, and manage their own AI projects throughout the course lifecycle. Classes are conducted thrice weekly with a maximum of 12 students. Graduates receive a recognized certificate. The program is available in English and Spanish. More information can be found at [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop